extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em Game Store], we sell games both digital and physical!

  h1 Dynamic content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p We have many games in our store as well as information about them and their developers!:

    ul
      li #[strong Games:] !{data.game_count}
      li #[strong Developers:] !{data.developer_count}
      li #[strong Publishers:] !{data.publisher_count}
      li #[strong Genres:] !{data.genre_count}
      li #[strong Platforms:] !{data.platform_count}
